{"tid":259551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冷氣技工昏迷製冷機房送院不治","createTime":"2017-05-27T04:39:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T04:48:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c4ae02f56692c69a3db4ba536ce13774a82e0ccb","tid":259551,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:39:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20035677&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170527\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20035677%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170527&d=d66SdBlJp1VENnazzFlDU%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=22c2dd70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20035677%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170527&h=1d28c6fd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20035677&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170527</a><br />\n<br />\n冷氣技工昏迷製冷機房<br />\n送院不治<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名返通宵班姓陳43歲冷氣技工，昨凌晨零時許，於鴨脷洲海怡西商場地下的製冷機房休息室等候工作期間，突感不適及陷於昏迷，工友發現報警。救護員到場替事主急救，惜送院不治。據稱死者已婚，有高血壓病歷紀錄。警方初步調查沒有可疑，死因有待剖屍化驗。<br />\n<br />\n97年主權移交至今，香港前進還是倒退？「蘋果」與你細數廿載風雨。<br />\n【回歸二十年】專頁：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhksar20.appledaily.com.hk&d=d66SdBlJp1VENnazzFlDU%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=46b2d636\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk</a>￼"},{"pid":"c3ca341a3eb3b12509c1ea1231a7ce07f56edb54","tid":259551,"uid":82068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:48:55.000Z","msg":"冷氣佬少一個冇一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}